<p>随着更多人获得高分辨率音频，高分辨率的价格也随之而来。您需要订阅 HiFi Plus 才能访问 FLAC 流，每月费用为 20 美元。潮汐<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tidal-is-increasing-its-hifi-plan-to-11-per-month-183139113.html">最近提高了标准订阅的价格，</a></ins>每月 10 美元到 11 美元。有传言称行业领导者 Spotify 正在<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/spotify-may-finally-be-ready-to-launch-a-premium-hifi-audio-tier-123847826.html">准备自己的高保真音响层。</a></ins></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tidal-adds-hi-res-flac-streaming-for-hifi-plus-subscribers-164540463.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tidal-adds-hi-res-flac-streaming-for-hifi-plus-subscribers-164540463.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ff190bf5-2c1b-4b0f-acf6-85ea3fba23fe</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jul 2023 16:45:40 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688573692</ingested><modified> 2023-07-05T16:14:56+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="630" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/de07a9e0-1b4d-11ee-adf7-83fb1abafb52" width="1200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="630" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/de07a9e0-1b4d-11ee-adf7-83fb1abaf