tron-focuses-on-luxury-over-performance-133217104.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 18d0b392-4299-4eaa-9487-7ad22c6fd5d0</guid><dc:creator>罗伯托·鲍德温</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jul 2023 13:32:17 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688563938</ingested><modified> 2023-07-05T13:32:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Roberto Baldwin]]></category><media:content height="1350" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/73538a30-1b37-11ee-b637-30c173e48152" width="2400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1350" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/73538a30-1b37-11ee-b637-30c173e48152" width="2400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Roberto Baldwin for Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Audi Q8 E-Tron]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Audi Q8 E-Tron]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>